WEBVTT

00:00:00.057 --> 00:00:00.864
vegn

00:00:00.864 --> 00:00:02.071
bahaltn zikh

00:00:02.099 --> 00:00:04.923
unter a bet in Sokolov.

00:00:04.664 --> 00:00:05.232
ye

00:00:04.923 --> 00:00:08.844
ven di natsis zaynen gekumen tsu nemen di mentshn tsu Treblinke.

00:00:09.980 --> 00:00:12.505
mit vemen hostu zikh bahaltn mit?

00:00:13.810 --> 00:00:15.273
ikh bin aroys

00:00:16.291 --> 00:00:17.821
oyf di gas

00:00:20.020 --> 00:00:23.559
tsu antloyfn, avektsugeyn, heyst es.

00:00:23.210 --> 00:00:24.217
aleyn?

00:00:24.205 --> 00:00:25.128
aleyn.

00:00:26.399 --> 00:00:28.851
vos iz geshen mit di mamen?

00:00:27.732 --> 00:00:30.506
i- bin ikh, bin ikh, a- yo zey,

00:00:30.506 --> 00:00:34.201
UNK di di di di mame un ale

00:00:34.201 --> 00:00:39.483
hobn z- zenen avek in Treblinke, zey hobn dokh avekgenumen, nor ikh bin geblibn untern bet, bin ikh aroysge-

00:00:39.483 --> 00:00:42.762
avekgegagnen fun untern bet un ikh bin tsugegangen tsum fentster,

00:00:44.135 --> 00:00:46.897
ikh hob gezen vi zey trinken di vaser

00:00:48.978 --> 00:00:51.734
un se gevezn

00:00:51.734 --> 00:00:53.967
a shrek tsu kukn vi azoy ale

00:00:54.108 --> 00:00:57.573
di fir un fertsik mentshn, mayn shvester iz oykh dort geven,

00:00:57.573 --> 00:01:02.523
zi iz nakher antlofn, me hot a- me hot gezen a yung meydl hot men ir genumen tsu der arbet.

00:01:02.849 --> 00:01:05.645
iz zi nisht gegangen keyn Treblinke.

00:01:05.380 --> 00:01:07.265
Nome iz es geven?

00:01:06.393 --> 00:01:07.619
Nome'n, yo.

00:01:09.667 --> 00:01:14.909
un me hot ir genumen tsu der arbet, un z- zi geyt, zey hobn shoyn dort gegat fun fun frier,

00:01:15.269 --> 00:01:16.900
yunge khevre,

00:01:18.104 --> 00:01:20.900
un zi iz geven ongeton bloyz mit UNK

00:01:21.091 --> 00:01:22.334
a nakht-hemd,

00:01:22.964 --> 00:01:23.937
oyf zikh,

00:01:24.365 --> 00:01:25.422
nisht mer,

00:01:26.829 --> 00:01:27.746
un zi hot

00:01:27.746 --> 00:01:30.249
gearbet ibern tog,

00:01:32.009 --> 00:01:33.269
a voser arbet,

00:01:33.697 --> 00:01:35.463
ikh veys afile nisht,

00:01:36.717 --> 00:01:39.226
bay nakht iz zi antlofn

00:01:40.852 --> 00:01:42.685
durkh toyte mentshn

00:01:42.860 --> 00:01:45.757
iz zi antlofn ven se geven fintster bay nakht,

00:01:46.471 --> 00:01:48.035
un zi avek

00:01:48.125 --> 00:01:49.739
nokh Sokolov

00:01:50.049 --> 00:01:53.789
i- i- iz geven aza dorf a kleyne dorf,

00:01:55.094 --> 00:01:59.037
un di, u- fun dort zenen gekumen oykhet kinder

00:02:00.562 --> 00:02:02.395
in SCHOOL arayn,

00:02:04.764 --> 00:02:05.635
ven mayn,

00:02:05.877 --> 00:02:08.791
t- vu mayn shvester iz gegangen in SCHOOL.

00:02:11.041 --> 00:02:14.405
hot zi gekent dort a

00:02:14.405 --> 00:02:15.541
a meydl,

00:02:16.593 --> 00:02:17.988
nisht a yidishe,

00:02:19.664 --> 00:02:25.312
un z- ven zi iz antlofn, se iz ir gelungen durkh di toyte mentshn tsu loyfn

00:02:25.368 --> 00:02:26.560
in der nakht,

00:02:27.612 --> 00:02:30.695
iz se nisht tsu gloybn az zi hot mir dos gezogt,

00:02:31.072 --> 00:02:33.448
un zi antlofn tsu diye

00:02:33.468 --> 00:02:36.027
meydl vos zi hot mit ir gezesn

00:02:36.320 --> 00:02:37.681
in SCHOOL.

00:02:38.750 --> 00:02:43.064
zi hot gevust vu zi voynt ober ikh hob nisht gevust vu.

00:02:43.914 --> 00:02:45.764
dos iz geven lebn Sokolov.

00:02:48.757 --> 00:02:51.991
vos iz geshen mit dir, du host ge- zikh bahaltn?

00:02:52.199 --> 00:02:54.050
vayter ikh gey dir dir zogn.

00:02:54.629 --> 00:02:56.446
se nisht gring tsu redn.

00:02:58.122 --> 00:03:03.280
un azoy vi ikh hob bashtimt vil avek fun geto,

00:03:05.784 --> 00:03:08.405
un ikh gey arop nokh a shtok

00:03:08.405 --> 00:03:09.257
ze ikh

00:03:09.257 --> 00:03:11.212
vi a yung vaybele

00:03:11.369 --> 00:03:13.456
kukt aroys durkhn fentster.

00:03:15.183 --> 00:03:17.661
i- ir, vi azoy hob ikh ir zezen? vayle

00:03:17.697 --> 00:03:21.826
ikh hob gekent dort di mentshn, zog ikh, ikh hob oyfgemakht di tir,

00:03:22.119 --> 00:03:23.412
barn aropgeyn

00:03:24.414 --> 00:03:25.049
i-

00:03:25.359 --> 00:03:31.546
i- ikh, get a makh oyf di tir, un un zi zitst un kukt aroys durkhn fentster, dos vel ikh keyn mol nisht fargesn,

00:03:31.636 --> 00:03:33.588
un zi hot zikh dershrokn shtark,

00:03:35.028 --> 00:03:36.797
zog ikh, "hob nisht keyn moyre,"

00:03:36.797 --> 00:03:37.638
zog ikh far-

00:03:37.846 --> 00:03:40.237
zi fregt zikh mir, fun vanet nem ikh mir do?

00:03:41.086 --> 00:03:42.447
hob ikh ir gezogt,

00:03:42.723 --> 00:03:46.413
az me hot, me hot mir yetst aropgenumen fir un fertsik mentshn,

00:03:46.824 --> 00:03:50.530
dos iz geven der, oyfn eleftn tog, ven me hot shoyn nisht getort ekzistirn,

00:03:51.262 --> 00:03:53.349
un zi hot gezogt, ikh kuk aroys,

00:03:53.455 --> 00:03:57.331
un fun ir, fun ir tsimer, zey hobn gemakht a topele vant

00:03:57.556 --> 00:03:59.561
iz geven dray geshtorbn,

00:03:59.581 --> 00:04:01.432
nor zi lebt nokh.

00:04:01.927 --> 00:04:03.558
un ir man

00:04:08.069 --> 00:04:11.523
ir man hot men genumen tsuzamen

00:04:11.900 --> 00:04:15.370
tsu der arbet, tsu der rusishn grenets mit mayn bruder.

00:04:15.646 --> 00:04:16.529
un zi hot

00:04:16.574 --> 00:04:19.364
un zi hot bashtimt zi geyt dort ts-

00:04:19.364 --> 00:04:20.399
tsum man.

00:04:31.036 --> 00:04:32.954
vos host, di froy hot zikh

00:04:33.365 --> 00:04:36.245
geshrekn ven du host, ven zi hot dir gezen

00:04:37.803 --> 00:04:40.711
zi hot nisht gevust ver es makht oyf di tir.

00:04:40.739 --> 00:04:42.489
iz zi gevorn dershrokn.

00:04:43.287 --> 00:04:47.804
ven zi hot mir derzen hot men shoyn tsu redn un mir, mir hobn zikh opgeshmuest

00:04:47.945 --> 00:04:49.525
az me iz, se se geven

00:04:50.155 --> 00:04:51.989
a moyre aroystugeyn,

00:04:52.248 --> 00:04:55.274
hot men zikh opgeshmuest, bay nakht zi hot gevust

00:04:55.285 --> 00:04:56.562
a ander

00:04:56.720 --> 00:04:59.392
veg aroystsugeyn. se ge- se gevezn

00:04:59.437 --> 00:05:02.789
a apteyk hot men dos gerufn. do ruft men a DRUG-STORE.

00:05:03.892 --> 00:05:06.631
i- iz me iz dort arumet aroysgegangen.

00:05:06.631 --> 00:05:08.234
zi iz gegan- un mir hobn zikh ge-

00:05:08.234 --> 00:05:10.192
tsukusht un mir hobn zikh gezegnt,

00:05:10.192 --> 00:05:13.910
zi iz gegangen avek in a ander veg, un ikh bin gegangen a ander veg.

00:05:16.582 --> 00:05:18.275
se mir azoy ayngefaln

00:05:18.320 --> 00:05:20.390
az ikh zol geyn mit dem veg

00:05:21.999 --> 00:05:25.216
vu me geyt fun Sokolov keyn Shedlets.

00:05:28.310 --> 00:05:32.759
ven ikh bin gegangen aroys iz geven nokh tunkl in der fri.

00:05:34.351 --> 00:05:37.315
ikh hob aropgenumen di len- di lente hob ikh nisht gehat,

00:05:38.300 --> 00:05:40.539
un ikh bin gegangen mit di gas

00:05:40.764 --> 00:05:43.812
azoy vi me geyt keyn Shedlets, di gas,

00:05:45.708 --> 00:05:47.710
un shtel zikh for

00:05:47.885 --> 00:05:49.837
ven ikh gey op a shtikl

00:05:49.927 --> 00:05:50.765
shoyn

00:05:51.108 --> 00:05:52.199
di shtot,

00:05:52.492 --> 00:05:55.254
fun di shtot avektsugeyn, fun Sokolov,

00:05:55.698 --> 00:05:58.409
geyt far mir fun der vaytns

00:05:59.208 --> 00:06:00.957
tsvey daytshn,

00:06:02.667 --> 00:06:04.045
mit gever,

00:06:04.405 --> 00:06:06.495
un ikh hob nisht gevolt antloyfn,

00:06:06.495 --> 00:06:07.606
ikh hob moyre gehat,

00:06:08.523 --> 00:06:12.517
⟨ikh⟩ bin ikh, hob ikh ayngeshtelt mayn lebn, ikh bin gegangen glaykh.

00:06:13.029 --> 00:06:14.671
zey zenen gegangen

00:06:14.682 --> 00:06:18.451
in dem veg tsu mir un ikh bin gegangen in dem veg

00:06:18.451 --> 00:06:19.587
tsu zey.

00:06:20.369 --> 00:06:23.401
ven ikh bin gekumen shoyn noent tsu zey,

00:06:24.048 --> 00:06:25.544
hot mayn harts

00:06:25.786 --> 00:06:26.945
geklapt

00:06:27.085 --> 00:06:28.753
i- az me hot gekent zeen

00:06:28.753 --> 00:06:30.775
fun der vaytsn, gloyb ikh.

00:06:31.524 --> 00:06:33.056
ikh kum tsu,

00:06:33.076 --> 00:06:34.555
m- mir,

00:06:34.932 --> 00:06:37.301
zey blaybn shteyn lebn mir un ikh

00:06:37.329 --> 00:06:38.347
blayb shteyen

00:06:38.347 --> 00:06:39.905
un zey fregn zikh mir,

00:06:41.328 --> 00:06:42.706
"bistu YUDE?"

00:06:46.947 --> 00:06:48.832
tu ikh, tu ikh a zog,

00:06:49.107 --> 00:06:50.485
in poylish,

00:06:50.643 --> 00:06:51.886
"vos zogstu?"

00:06:55.115 --> 00:06:56.510
ober in poylish.

00:06:57.309 --> 00:07:00.864
fregt zikh mir nokh a mol, "bistu YUDE?" mit aaz geshrey.

00:07:01.612 --> 00:07:03.175
zog ikh nokh a mol,

00:07:03.519 --> 00:07:05.690
"ikh farshtey nisht vos du zogst,"

00:07:06.303 --> 00:07:07.529
in poylish.

00:07:08.007 --> 00:07:09.385
der tsveyter

00:07:09.948 --> 00:07:13.098
hot gekent epes poylish, a tsubrokhenem,

00:07:13.779 --> 00:07:15.528
fregt er zikh mir,

00:07:16.968 --> 00:07:18.430
"vu voynstu?"

00:07:20.967 --> 00:07:22.278
in poylish.

00:07:23.060 --> 00:07:23.943
vayz ikh

00:07:23.943 --> 00:07:25.057
mit di hant

00:07:25.102 --> 00:07:28.150
"ot do," se dort geven dort etlekhe shtubn,

00:07:28.240 --> 00:07:29.433
zog ikh, "do,"

00:07:29.945 --> 00:07:31.424
vayz ikh mit der hant.

00:07:33.961 --> 00:07:35.609
un shtel zikh for,

00:07:35.902 --> 00:07:37.921
un zey lozn mir geyn avek.

00:07:39.715 --> 00:07:42.849
hob ikh opgeziftst, zog ikh "riboyne-sheloylem,

00:07:45.352 --> 00:07:46.747
se mir gelungen!"

00:07:47.849 --> 00:07:49.683
un ikh bin avekgeganen.

00:07:50.245 --> 00:07:52.242
un dos harts hot nisht gekla-

00:07:53.553 --> 00:07:54.864
geSTOPt klapn.

00:07:56.439 --> 00:07:59.302
ikh gey un ikh gey, zog ikh tsu mir, "vu gey ikh?

00:08:00.134 --> 00:08:01.850
ikh veys do nisht keynemen."

00:08:04.404 --> 00:08:06.898
biz se mir ayngefaln, ikh hob mir dermant

00:08:06.898 --> 00:08:07.925
az mayn

00:08:08.167 --> 00:08:09.562
mayn shvester

00:08:10.765 --> 00:08:13.021
iz gegangen do mit eyner

00:08:13.550 --> 00:08:15.772
in SCHOOL, efsher iz

00:08:16.165 --> 00:08:17.909
efsher iz durkh a tsufal,

00:08:17.920 --> 00:08:19.383
hob ikh azoy getrakht,

00:08:20.165 --> 00:08:22.100
efsher durkh a tsufal iz

00:08:22.274 --> 00:08:24.867
iz zi dort, efsher vos.

00:08:26.493 --> 00:08:29.609
un ikh bin geven dorshtik, hungerik oykhet.

00:08:30.172 --> 00:08:33.257
nu nem gey on a adres, on a nomen,

00:08:33.257 --> 00:08:34.739
nor ikh hob nor gevust

00:08:35.875 --> 00:08:37.557
az dos meydl

00:08:38.137 --> 00:08:39.734
hot geheysn YADZHE,

00:08:40.938 --> 00:08:42.755
mer hob ikh gornisht gevust.

00:08:45.410 --> 00:08:47.075
nem zukh a YADZHE.

00:08:47.249 --> 00:08:48.656
se iz epes

00:08:48.667 --> 00:08:49.809
vunderlekh.

00:08:53.493 --> 00:08:54.545
gey ikh ⟨aykh⟩

00:08:54.545 --> 00:08:56.021
tsu nenter

00:08:56.058 --> 00:08:57.925
tsu di shtubn,

00:08:58.117 --> 00:09:00.308
ze ikh vi a man, nisht a-

00:09:00.308 --> 00:09:01.278
a krist,

00:09:01.306 --> 00:09:01.959
geyt

00:09:02.217 --> 00:09:05.637
mit tsvey groyse kibles, er geyt nokh vaser,

00:09:06.672 --> 00:09:09.839
tsu der brune, se geven a brune, veyst vos heyst a brune?

00:09:10.267 --> 00:09:11.999
vos me shept di vaser.

00:09:15.852 --> 00:09:19.188
bin ikh tsugegangen tsu im un ikh freg im oyf poylish,

00:09:19.345 --> 00:09:21.213
"tsu veystu nisht do

00:09:21.640 --> 00:09:24.633
vu es voynt ikh veys nisht," zog ikh, "dem nomen,

00:09:24.644 --> 00:09:27.389
nor di tokhter hot geheysn YADZHE."

00:09:28.694 --> 00:09:30.750
"oh!" zogt, zogt er, "YADZHE?

00:09:30.750 --> 00:09:33.498
oh, zi voynt do un do, mayne visn."

00:09:35.140 --> 00:09:38.428
ikh gey tsu un ikh klap on di tir,

00:09:38.465 --> 00:09:40.349
kumt aroys a froy,

00:09:40.726 --> 00:09:42.087
a kristlekhe,

00:09:42.498 --> 00:09:45.479
un zi kukt on. zi ken mir nisht, ikh ken ir nisht.

00:09:46.818 --> 00:09:50.120
zog ikh ir, "dayn tokhter heyst YADZHE?"

00:09:50.446 --> 00:09:51.706
zogt zi, "yo."

00:09:52.741 --> 00:09:55.199
zog ikh, "ken ikh, ken ikh redn tsun ir?"

00:09:55.492 --> 00:09:58.996
tut zi a geshrey, "YADZHE" kum do ts- me ruft dir."

00:09:59.299 --> 00:10:00.222
in poylish?

00:10:00.256 --> 00:10:01.477
in poylish.

00:10:04.790 --> 00:10:09.526
un zi kumt zir, zi hot mir gekent, vayle zi, mayn shvester hot ir a mol ayngeladnt

00:10:09.599 --> 00:10:13.255
far a CUP OF TEA, tsi COFFEE, epes fun di SCHOOL.

00:10:14.611 --> 00:10:16.141
un zi derkent mir,

00:10:18.070 --> 00:10:19.932
tut zi a, loyft tsu tsu mir

00:10:19.932 --> 00:10:21.153
khapt mir on

00:10:21.344 --> 00:10:21.932
un

00:10:21.935 --> 00:10:22.953
un zogt mir,

00:10:22.953 --> 00:10:24.174
"veyst vos?" zogt

00:10:24.955 --> 00:10:26.463
zogt zi,

00:10:26.463 --> 00:10:28.156
"dayn shvester iz do do!"

00:10:29.613 --> 00:10:31.736
zog ikh, "mayn shvester iz do do?"

00:10:31.736 --> 00:10:33.320
ven iz zi gekumen?"

00:10:33.511 --> 00:10:35.615
zogt zi, "nekhtn bay der nakht."

00:10:37.612 --> 00:10:39.412
tak shtel zikh for!

00:10:40.109 --> 00:10:44.221
dem vunder vos ikh hob gehat, se nisht tsu gloybn geven!

00:10:46.302 --> 00:10:49.874
nu zi zi zogt mir, "ober zi hot nisht vos ontsutun."

00:10:51.652 --> 00:10:53.024
"i- vu iz zi?"

00:10:53.024 --> 00:10:54.532
zogt zi, "oyfn boydem."

00:10:54.706 --> 00:10:56.332
zog ikh, "ken ikh ir zeen?"

00:10:56.332 --> 00:11:00.624
zi hot tsugebrengt aza leyter, vu me krikht aroyf, mit di fis aroyf,

00:11:02.469 --> 00:11:08.234
un ikh krikh a- ikh krikh aroyf, un zi zogt shoyn der mame in poylish ver ikh bin,

00:11:08.999 --> 00:11:10.951
az zi ken mayn shvester,

00:11:11.446 --> 00:11:14.799
un ikh gey aroyf, se se fintster nokh gevezn,

00:11:16.340 --> 00:11:17.870
un ikh zog, "Nome!"

00:11:17.977 --> 00:11:20.418
un zi hot mir derhert, kumt zi tsu,

00:11:20.542 --> 00:11:22.224
un ikh gey aroyf,

00:11:26.380 --> 00:11:29.272
iz zi zogt, "vi azoy bistu do do?!

00:11:29.317 --> 00:11:30.765
vi azoy bistu gekumen?"

00:11:30.765 --> 00:11:32.416
hob ikh ir gezogt vi azoy.

00:11:34.767 --> 00:11:37.664
nokh ⟨dem⟩ zogt zi, "veyst az ikh hob nisht vos ontsutun?"

00:11:39.054 --> 00:11:40.806
un shtel zikh for,

00:11:40.806 --> 00:11:42.097
ven ikh bin an-

00:11:42.142 --> 00:11:44.769
aroys fun untern bet, vi ikh hob dir gezogt,

00:11:45.955 --> 00:11:47.759
bin ikh arayngegangen

00:11:47.759 --> 00:11:49.021
in undzer ROOM,

00:11:50.326 --> 00:11:52.345
ikh zol kenen epes

00:11:52.705 --> 00:11:55.164
esn, eps vos gefinen,

00:11:55.810 --> 00:11:57.391
hob ikh gefunen nokh

00:11:58.764 --> 00:12:03.685
a, hob ikh nokh gefunen epes a por UNK, hob ikh gegangen ikh hob genumen eyn UNK,

00:12:04.248 --> 00:12:08.709
u a lefl mel, dos ikh gedenk ikh, ikh vel keyn mol nisht fargesn,

00:12:08.709 --> 00:12:09.882
ikh hob oysgemisht,

00:12:09.882 --> 00:12:11.535
ikh hob genumen a bisl vaser,

00:12:11.535 --> 00:12:13.417
un aroyfgeshtelt in a tepele,

00:12:13.417 --> 00:12:16.510
un ikh hob es farkokht un ikh hob aroyfgegosn aza tripekhts,

00:12:17.765 --> 00:12:19.194
un veyst vos?

00:12:19.773 --> 00:12:21.610
ikh hob nisht gekent aropshlingen,

00:12:21.610 --> 00:12:23.109
ikh hob nisht gegesn,

00:12:23.199 --> 00:12:24.948
ikh hob nor oysgetrunken

00:12:25.173 --> 00:12:28.559
di flisigkeyt hob ikh oysgetrunken, UNK farkokht,

00:12:28.767 --> 00:12:30.854
ikh hob nisht gekent aropshlingen.

00:12:31.434 --> 00:12:32.829
volstu gegloybt?

00:12:33.577 --> 00:12:36.710
ikh hob nisht ge- ikh hob nisht gevust az ikh ken nisht shlingen!

